entries.title: Lil Tecca "Ransom" (Live Performance) | Open Mic
entries.description:
Lil Tecca recently stopped by Genius for a live performance of his breakout hit, “Ransom,” which has racked up an impressive 50 million YouTube views to date. The track is produced by Nick Mira & Taz Taylor.

Read more on Genius: https://genius.com/a/lil-tecca-performs-ransom-live-at-genius

Read all the lyrics to "Ransom" on Genius: https://genius.com/Lil-tecca-ransom-lyrics

Watch the official music video for "Ransom": https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XzY2ij_vL4

entries.title: IV JAY “Love Song” (Live Performance) | Open Mic
entries.description:
Singer-songwriter IV JAY is the latest artist to appear on Open Mic, performing her hit, “Love Song” in partnership with eBay. The track has racked up 3 million Spotify streams to date and appears on her 2020 EP \'5th Element.\' During her performance, the New Jersey native croons about the struggles of writing a love song.

Read more on Genius: https://genius.com/a/iv-jay-performs-love-song-live
Read all the lyrics to "Love Song" on Genius: https://genius.com/Iv-jay-love-song-lyrics
Watch the official music video for "Love Song": https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4L6Py-JdcM0
